  <li> Registr&aacute;cia &quot;extra z&aacute;ruky&quot; mus&iacute; by&#357; uskuto&#269;nen&aacute; najnesk&ocirc;r do 28 dn&iacute; od d&aacute;tumu n&aacute;kupu.</li>
