<h3>&#268;AS&#356; 3 - Extra z&aacute;ruka</h3>
<p>Vytla&#269;te si toto potvrdenie o registr&aacute;cii alebo si ho ulo&#382;te vo svojom po&#269;&iacute;ta&#269;i. &quot;Extra z&aacute;ruka&quot; bude uznan&aacute; iba vtedy, ak spolu s dokladom o zak&uacute;pen&iacute; v&yacute;robku predlo&#382;&iacute;te vytla&#269;en&eacute; potvrdenie o registr&aacute;cii svojho v&yacute;robku.                                                                                            S roz&scaron;&iacute;renou z&aacute;ru&#269;nou dobou z&iacute;skate n&aacute;rok na uznanie rovnak&yacute;ch reklam&aacute;ci&iacute; ako s be&#382;nou z&aacute;ru&#269;nou dobou. Tieto podmienky a kontakt v pr&iacute;slu&scaron;nej krajine n&aacute;jdete v z&aacute;ru&#269;nom liste, n&aacute;vode a prostredn&iacute;ctvom Russell Hobbs webov&yacute;ch str&aacute;nok <a href="http://www.russellhobbs.com/register/" target="_blank">www.russellhobbs.com/register/</a>.</p>
