<li>E-mailov&eacute; newslettery bud&uacute; obsahova&#357; aktu&aacute;lne  ponuky, novinky a inform&aacute;cie t&yacute;kaj&uacute;ce sa na&scaron;ich produktov. Neust&aacute;le sa sna&#382;&iacute;me vylep&scaron;ova&#357; na&scaron;e slu&#382;by. Toto zah&#341;&#328;a i anal&yacute;zu e-mailov&yacute;ch newsletterov, ktor&eacute; boli odoslan&eacute;, napr&iacute;klad &#269;i s&uacute; poskytnut&eacute; e-mailov&eacute; adresy dostupn&eacute;, &#269;i bol newsletter otvoren&yacute; v ur&#269;itom &#269;ase, ktor&eacute; odkazy z newsletterov boli otvoren&eacute; alebo &#269;i existuje nejak&aacute; sp&auml;tn&aacute; v&auml;zba &#269;i odpove&#271;. </li>
<li>V bud&uacute;cnosti m&aacute;te pr&aacute;vo sa odhl&aacute;si&#357; z odoberania e-mailov&yacute;ch newsletterov a to kedyko&#318;vek a s okam&#382;itou &uacute;&#269;innos&#357;ou. Toto je mo&#382;n&eacute; uskuto&#269;ni&#357; kliknut&iacute;m na odkaz pre odhl&aacute;senie v spodnej &#269;asti na&scaron;ich e-mailov&yacute;ch newsletterov alebo n&aacute;s m&ocirc;&#382;ete kontaktova&#357; prostredn&iacute;ctvom kontaktn&eacute;ho formul&aacute;ra na webe alebo na   <a href="mailto:info@eu.spectrumbrands.com">info@eu.spectrumbrands.com</a>. </li>
